claim.claim-text:
1. One or more computer-readable media having computer-useable instructions embodied thereon for performing a method of reaching a position in an ordered list of items on a display that are stored in a mobile communications device, the method comprising:
presenting the ordered list of items on the display of the mobile communications device, the list of items having a first subset of related items and a second subset of related items;
presenting a selectable option on the display of the mobile communications device, wherein the selectable option is selectable by way of a touch action to the selectable option;
incident to receiving an indication that the selectable option is selected, presenting a positional indicator that indicates a first corresponding position within the ordered list by way of information displayed within the positional indicator, wherein the information displayed within the positional indicator indicates the first subset of related items without specifying the related items within the first subset; and
incident to moving the selectable option from a first position to a second position, the information displayed within the positional indicator is modified to indicate a second corresponding position within the ordered list by indicating the second subset of related items without specifying the related items within the second subset.
